<i>[Man Narrating] Michael came home</i>
<i>to find his brother-in-law Tobias...</i>

00:23.723 --> 00:27.386
- <i>who'd been kicked out of</i>
<i>the house earlier that week.</i>
- How are you?

00:27.494 --> 00:29.394
- [Chuckles]
- Good.

00:29.496 --> 00:32.293
