<i>that pot-addled mind ofhis.</i>

02:58.278 --> 03:01.736
Anyway, it's a party,
and I want the whole family there.

03:01.848 --> 03:04.078
- We're havin' a party?
- No.

03:04.184 --> 03:08.848
<i>Well, I'm sorry if I don't want you</i>
<i>doing one of your stupid puppet shows.</i>

03:08.955 --> 03:12.914
I did that once, Mom.
And a lot of people thought it was pretty cool.

03:13.026 --> 03:15.085
<i>[Narrator]</i>
<i>In an effort to hip up his act...</i>

03:15.195 --> 03:17.356
