Marry me!

10:23.422 --> 10:26.391
Hey, I'm almost done with that coverage.
I can bring it to you tonight.

10:26.492 --> 10:28.392
Are you still
at the Balboa Towers?

10:28.494 --> 10:31.122
<i>[Narrator]</i>
<i>Maeby had used her grandmother's address...</i>

10:31.230 --> 10:33.130
<i>so as not to arouse</i>
<i>suspicion at home.</i>

10:33.232 --> 10:36.497
