and roll the windows down, please?

11:41.500 --> 11:44.628
I'm just messin' with you. Hey, Franklin.
How you doin', little man?

11:48.174 --> 11:50.267
So I'm afraid Ann's
with my husband.

11:50.376 --> 11:52.435
