vow renewal at the chapel.

11:52.545 --> 11:55.480
<i>[Narrator]</i>
<i>A call that was made by George Sr.</i>

11:55.581 --> 11:58.209
How do we get her to the church?
Tell her you're in here?

11:58.317 --> 12:00.911
