and take her to the limo.

12:01.020 --> 12:04.786
No. Bring her in here, knock her out with this
ether, and you stuff her into this garment bag.

12:04.890 --> 12:08.121
Anyone sees, you do the same.
Oh, hi, Tobias.

12:08.227 --> 12:10.127
Oh.

12:10.229 --> 12:13.721
Whenever I get a wee bit scared
I hum a little tune

12:13.833 --> 12:15.733
Hum diddle diddly
Hum di-do

12:15.835 --> 12:18.497
You put a handkerchief over her mouth
for a couple of seconds.

12:18.604 --> 12:20.629
No more than two though.
'Cause you could kill her.

12:20.740 --> 12:22.298
- I don't have a handkerchief.
- Fine.

12:22.408 --> 12:25.809
Put the ether on the puppet's lips.
Have the puppet kiss her.

12:25.911 --> 12:27.902
I ain't kissin'
that old bitch.

12:28.013 --> 12:30.072
That's my wife, you bastard!

12:30.182 --> 12:32.173
Dad, that's my wrist!

12:32.284 --> 12:35.583
[Groaning]
Hey, man! That's his neck!

12:35.688 --> 12:38.851
Hey, Gob. Mrs. Veal,
this is my brother Gob.

12:38.958 --> 12:41.449
- Where's your pal Franklin?
- Throat's a little sore.

12:41.560 --> 12:44.028
And wrist.
Nice to meet you.

12:44.130 --> 12:46.155
